node.text:
Explore, live life and feel free 🤩When visiting Glacier National Park, you'll be spoiled for choice with the activities and beautiful natural sights you can bask in on this special day.

Besides hiking, biking, and camping, sightseeing is a must here. Its famous colorful rocks are a joy to witness, their unique colors determined by the presence or absence of iron. 🌈

What national parks have you visited? Any favourites you’d recommend 🤔

🎥 @go4theglobe
📍 Glacier National Park, Montana, US
🎶 Coastline - Hollow Coves

node.text:
Moments from the Maldives with @crewten Which of these images call to you the most?
Is it the dreamy sunsets, the crystal blue waters? The starry night, shooting hoops, lounging at your villa, or perhaps flipping off rocks or snorkeling with rays? 

No options are bad options and this place has it all! 🤩😍

Tag someone you want to experience this with 🙌

📷 @robinmaeter & @crewten

node.text:
How’s your commute to work on Mondays? 😅 This is a regular day for Mexico City’s Metro. 🚉 

Mexico City's extensive public transport system may seem overwhelming at first, but it is a fast and cheap way to get around once you get the hang of it. For a city with a population of over 20 million, efficient public transport is essential, and the Metro alone transports around five million people every day, the tenth-highest ridership of any metro system in the world.

Do you prefer leaving home for work or working from home? 

🎥 @metro_tok on TikTok
